<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink383">
<l>kōṭcurum paraṟṟu nāṭcurat tamaṉṟa</l>
<l>neṭuṅkāṉ marāattuk kuṟuñciṉai paṟṟi</l>
<l>valañcuri vāliṇar koytaṟku niṉṟa</l>
<l>maḷḷa ṉuḷḷa makiḻkūrn taṉṟē</l>
<l>pañcāyp pāvaikkun taṉakku</l>
<l>mañcāy kūnta lāyvatu kaṇṭē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>On seeing [the girl] combing hanging down tresses  </l>
<l>for herself and for the sedge grass doll, </l>
<l>the joy increased in the heart of a warrior,  </l>
<l>who stopped for plucking white right-whirling flower clusters, </l>
<l>bending down a short branch of a tall-trunked Kadamba tree,  </l>
<l>dense in the day desert, and swarmed by bees collecting [pollen]. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
